          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1699372392355-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>carrot ribbons</strong> and <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> in a large bowl with your <strong>white wine vinegar</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up - this is your <strong>carrot salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1699372396427-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1699372396427-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1699372396427-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1699372396427-x1000.jpg",
